Uses of Package
hu.elte.txtuml.api

  • Packages that use hu.elte.txtuml.api 
    Package Description
    hu.elte.txtuml.api
    Provides the txtUML modeling API.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend
    This package and its subpackages provide backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend.collections
    As a subpackage of hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend, provides backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend.collections.impl
    As a subpackage of hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend, provides backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend.messages
    As a subpackage of hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend, provides backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.blocks
    Contains functional interfaces to implement code blocks and condition evaluations in a txtUML model.
    hu.elte.txtuml.stdlib
    Contains the txtUML standard library which consists of external classes (subclasses of ExternalClass) that might be used to enhance the model with some special features which are not part of the standard UML2, like Timers.
